ALT + Arrows = switch text lines
HOME = to line beginning
END = to line end
CTRL + SHIFT + C/V = copy from/paste into bash terminal
CTRL + ALT + F3 = enter TTY (emergency shell where eventually run sudo reboot)
CTRL + ALT + F1 = return to GUI from TTY
ALT GR + Ã¬ = ~

Bash escape character = "\" (to escape "\", """, " ")
